CrossWords build tracker

Objective
- Create a polished crossword game from the PRD assumptions, commit it to the CrossWords repo, and prepare it for fantomzone.app deployment.

Assumptions
- The PRD was not present in the workspace, so the game is being built as a compact crossword-style puzzle collection with reusable mechanics.
- The repo was empty on arrival, so this is a greenfield scaffold.

Process log
- 2026-07-11: cloned repository and confirmed it had no commits.
- 2026-07-11: selected valid word-square puzzles to keep across and down answers consistent.
- 2026-07-11: built the game, verified the production build, and saved/deployed version 1 to Sites.
- 2026-07-11: added the `fantomzone.app` custom domain to the site; it is pending Cloudflare DNS validation records.
- 2026-07-11: local Git commit exists, but GitHub push is blocked by missing GitHub auth on this machine.
- 2026-07-11: fixed the deployed Sites 404 by embedding the Vite build assets directly in the worker and deployed version 2.
- 2026-07-11: rebuilt the game to match the intended PRD direction: word-search grid, word bank, swipe validation, hints, no timer, no penalties, themed progression, and brighter visual design.

Open questions
